and it's really great to meet everyone here.
This looks like an amazing community of people

3
00:10:30,290 --> 00:10:33,710
who genuinely support one another —

4
00:10:33,770 --> 00:10:37,050
you've built something really special here
that truly encourages creativity. That's remarkable.

5
