10
00:11:06,310 --> 00:11:09,410
So — a little about what I'm covering today.

11
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:13,350
I'm talking about scaling up lookbooks,

12
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:19,350
editorials, social content, and campaigns
for fashion, e-commerce, and DTC brands.

13
00:11:20,110 --> 00:11:23,590
Also joining me on this call are Daniel Ryan

14
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:26,260
and Sivan Aharon, who are part of our team.
Sivan made the video

15
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:40,050
