You're welcome to open a Workspace —
and try to work in a way

183
00:27:42,238 --> 00:27:45,858
where all your materials are organized
under one theme.

184
00:27:45,878 --> 00:27:48,798
I'd recommend trying it with a real concept —
take a brand you have in mind

185
00:27:48,798 --> 00:27:52,878
that you love, and experiment with something real.

186
00:27:52,878 --> 00:27:56,918
Think about a story — something special.
Try to create a concept that's unique.

187
00:27:56,958 --> 00:27:59,038
You can really go creative —
whether it's a farmers market

188
00:27:59,918 --> 00:28:10,178
